@page "/"

<PageTitle>Home</PageTitle>

<style>
    body {
        background-color: #f4f4f4; /* Light gray background for the whole page */
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        color: #333;
    }

    .container {
        width: 90%;
        max-width: 1200px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 20px;
    }

    h1 {
        color: #2e8b57; /* Forest green color for the heading */
        text-align: center;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .intro {
        text-align: center;
        margin-bottom: 40px;
        font-size: 1.2em;
        line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .highlight {
        background-color: #e9f5e9; /* Light green background for highlights */
        padding: 20px;
        border-radius: 8px;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

        .highlight h2 {
            color: #1e6f4c; /* Darker green color for the heading to enhance readability */
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

    .call-to-action {
        text-align: center;
        margin-top: 40px;
    }

        .call-to-action a {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 15px 30px;
            font-size: 1.2em;
            color: #fff;
            background-color: #2e8b57; /* Forest green button color */
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            transition: background-color 0.3s;
        }

            .call-to-action a:hover {
                background-color: #1e6f4c; /* Darker green on hover */
            }

    .img-responsive {
        width: 100%;
        height: auto;
        border-radius: 8px;
    }
</style>


<div class="container">
    <h1>Hello, Nature Lovers!</h1>

    <div class="intro">
        <p><strong>BE WITH NATURE, VISIT US</strong></p>
        <p>Discover the Gems of Region 12, also known as Soccsksargen, a vibrant and diverse region in the Philippines that promises an unforgettable adventure for every traveler. Nestled in the southern part of Mindanao, Region 12 offers a rich tapestry of landscapes, cultural heritage, and local charm, making it a hidden gem waiting to be explored.</p>
    </div>

    <div class>
        <h2>Why Visit Region 12?</h2>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Stunning Natural Landscapes:</strong> From rolling hills and verdant rice fields to pristine beaches and majestic waterfalls.</li>
            <li><strong>Cultural Richness:</strong> Immerse yourself in local heritage through colorful festivals, traditional dances, and unique culinary experiences.</li>
            <li><strong>Adventurous Escapades:</strong> Engage in thrilling outdoor activities like hiking, white-water rafting, and exploring hidden caves.</li>
            <li><strong>Warm Hospitality:</strong> Experience the genuine kindness of the locals and enjoy charming accommodations.</li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="call-to-action">
        <p>Ready to start your adventure?</p>
        <a href="/explore">Explore the Wonders of Region 12</a>
    </div>
</div>
